#: ../nitrophone/apps.rst:61
msgid "Backup: The integrated backup (Seedvault) and Nextcloud. Choose Settings -> System -> Backup."
msgstr ""
"Copia de seguridad: La copia de seguridad integrada (Seedvault) y Nextcloud. "
